{"tid":1080371,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"等緊做電療","createTime":"2019-03-27T14:15:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-27T14:28:02.000Z","uid":15647,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"163c87083a65d9145ac5ce0a20782d7e4d5e11d3","tid":1080371,"uid":15647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T14:15:53.000Z","msg":"以後內容有所刪改，可能會前後矛盾<br />\n<br />\n是咁的，捱過左大半年既化療，醫生話情況幾好，可以唔再化療轉做電療。因為之前由發現中招到化療實在快到連驚既時間都未有。到上星期見完醫生，依家等緊下一次再見醫生先知電療點做，但見到等候做化療既平均日數係二十幾日，而我問醫生大慨幾時先會做到電療都未有答案。<br />\n<br />\n所以想問下，係咪約電療要等好耐先排隊排到我?"},{"pid":"82a111e30e0619db69ce586f916a53b2a6bcf200","tid":1080371,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T14:21:09.000Z","msg":"咩事電療？"},{"pid":"ec83eab71440b2fbfe4dc1d3100dd3575bbb3a05","tid":1080371,"uid":15647,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"82a111e30e0619db69ce586f916a53b2a6bcf200","tid":1080371,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T14:21:09.000Z","msg":"咩事電療？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T14:24:13.000Z","msg":"淋巴癌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad96973e9d1cf7296817fb3d4dcd500a02717cb1","tid":1080371,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec83eab71440b2fbfe4dc1d3100dd3575bbb3a05","tid":1080371,"uid":15647,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"82a111e30e0619db69ce586f916a53b2a6bcf200","tid":1080371,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T14:21:09.000Z","msg":"咩事電療？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T14:24:13.000Z","msg":"淋巴癌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T14:25:53.000Z","msg":"嘩！早日康復<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e139fef92b7242ef72238a93ec302ec7c8e14e8","tid":1080371,"uid":15647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad96973e9d1cf7296817fb3d4dcd500a02717cb1","tid":1080371,"uid":18569,"